Resume Match: 60%

Explanation: The candidate possesses many of the necessary .NET skills (ASP.NET, MVC, C#, Entity Framework, SQL Server) and demonstrates experience in web application development. However, the resume shows only 3 years of experience, significantly less than the 4-7 years required. Furthermore, the job description emphasizes experience with REST services and Azure, which are mentioned in the resume indirectly but lack specific demonstrable experience. The candidate's experience with Python and React, while valuable, isn't directly relevant to the core .NET requirements of this role. The use of Java is positive but not directly reflected in the project descriptions.
